A-H, Neg-D, and L-mode scenarios have approached\ndivertor-compatible high separatrix density conditions, with Neg-D preserving\nthe highest performance owing to its compatibility with both high power and\ndensity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Dec 2020 17:47:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-04"}
