e good agreement for 6 out of the 10 modelled systems, where the relative\ndifference between observed and simulated final planet orbit is $\\leq 10\\%$,\nstrongly supports the idea that planet migration in the disc brought the\nplanets to their present locations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Dec 2020 13:07:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-13"}
