$\nconversion probability in the Sun. We used this result to evaluate the\nsensitivity of future experiments, notably the Super-Kamiokande Gadolinium\n(SK-Gd) upgrade.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Dec 2020 15:48:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2020 04:07:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 17 Mar 2022 10:27:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-18"}
